{"\u00deegar framkv\u00e6md sem fellur undir m\u00e1lsme\u00f0fer\u00f0 skv.[MAYBE-SPLIT]IV. kafla kallar jafnframt \u00e1 skipulagsger\u00f0 \u00e1 grundvelli skipulagslaga er heimilt a\u00f0 sameina sk\u00fdrsluger\u00f0 um umhverfismat framkv\u00e6mdarinnar samkv\u00e6mt l\u00f6gum \u00feessum og sk\u00fdrsluger\u00f0 um umhverfismat skipulagstill\u00f6gunnar samkv\u00e6mt l\u00f6gum \u00feessum og skipulagsl\u00f6gum.": false, "Senda skal[MAYBE-SPLIT]N\u00e1tt\u00faruverndarstofnun afrit af \u00fatgefnu leyfi til framkv\u00e6mda sem fela \u00ed s\u00e9r sker\u00f0ingu \u00e1 fri\u00f0u\u00f0u vistkerfi e\u00f0a vistger\u00f0 e\u00f0a b\u00fasv\u00e6\u00f0i fri\u00f0a\u00f0rar tegundar.": false, "Senda skal[MAYBE-SPLIT]N\u00e1tt\u00faruverndarstofnun afrit af \u00fatgefnu leyfi.": false, "\u00c1\u00f0ur en \u00e1kv\u00f6r\u00f0un um sl\u00edka sv\u00e6\u00f0askiptingu er tekin skal r\u00e1\u00f0herra m.a. afla umsagna Fiskistofu, Hafranns\u00f3knastofnunar, Landhelgisg\u00e6slu \u00cdslands, Matv\u00e6lastofnunar, N\u00e1tt\u00farufr\u00e6\u00f0istofnunar \u00cdslands,[MAYBE-SPLIT]Samg\u00f6ngustofu, Umhverfis- og orkustofnunar og vi\u00f0komandi sveitarstj\u00f3rnar.": false, "Einnig skal r\u00e1\u00f0herra afla umsagna Fiskistofu, Hafranns\u00f3knastofnunar, Landhelgisg\u00e6slu \u00cdslands, Matv\u00e6lastofnunar, N\u00e1tt\u00farufr\u00e6\u00f0istofnunar \u00cdslands,[MAYBE-SPLIT]Samg\u00f6ngustofu, Umhverfis- og orkustofnunar og vi\u00f0komandi sveitarstj\u00f3rnar.": false, "\u00c1\u00f0ur en tilraunaleyfi er veitt skal Matv\u00e6lastofnun afla umsagna Fiskistofu, Hafranns\u00f3knastofnunar, Landhelgisg\u00e6slu \u00cdslands,[MAYBE-SPLIT]Samg\u00f6ngustofu, Umhverfis- og orkustofnunar og vi\u00f0komandi sveitarstj\u00f3rnar um hvort n\u00e1tt\u00farulegar a\u00f0st\u00e6\u00f0ur \u00e1 fyrirhugu\u00f0u tilraunasv\u00e6\u00f0i e\u00f0a fyrirhuga\u00f0ar tegundir, stofnar e\u00f0a starfsa\u00f0fer\u00f0ir gefi tilefni til h\u00e6ttu \u00e1 neikv\u00e6\u00f0um vistfr\u00e6\u00f0i- e\u00f0a erf\u00f0afr\u00e6\u00f0i\u00e1hrifum sem leitt getur af leyfisskyldri starfsemi.": false, "\u00c1\u00f0ur en r\u00e6ktunarleyfi er veitt skal Matv\u00e6lastofnun afla umsagna Fiskistofu, Hafranns\u00f3knastofnunar, N\u00e1tt\u00farufr\u00e6\u00f0istofnunar \u00cdslands,[MAYBE-SPLIT]Samg\u00f6ngustofu, Umhverfis- og orkustofnunar og vi\u00f0komandi sveitarstj\u00f3rnar um hvort n\u00e1tt\u00farulegar a\u00f0st\u00e6\u00f0ur \u00e1 fyrirhugu\u00f0u r\u00e6ktunarsv\u00e6\u00f0i e\u00f0a fyrirhuga\u00f0ar tegundir, stofnar e\u00f0a starfsa\u00f0fer\u00f0ir gefi tilefni til h\u00e6ttu \u00e1 neikv\u00e6\u00f0um vistfr\u00e6\u00f0i- e\u00f0a erf\u00f0afr\u00e6\u00f0i\u00e1hrifum sem leitt getur af leyfisskyldri starfsemi.": false, "\u00cd r\u00e1\u00f0gjafarnefnd fagstofnana og eftirlitsa\u00f0ila skulu vera m.a. fulltr\u00faar fr\u00e1[MAYBE-SPLIT]N\u00e1tt\u00faruverndarstofnun, Ve\u00f0urstofu \u00cdslands, Skipulagsstofnun, Fiskistofu, Hafranns\u00f3knastofnun, Samg\u00f6ngustofu, Landi og sk\u00f3gi, N\u00e1tt\u00farufr\u00e6\u00f0istofnun, Matv\u00e6lastofnun, H\u00fasn\u00e6\u00f0is- og mannvirkjastofnun, Vegager\u00f0inni, n\u00e1tt\u00farustofum og heilbrig\u00f0iseftirliti sveitarf\u00e9laga.": false, "\u00cd r\u00e1\u00f0gjafarnefnd fagstofnana og eftirlitsa\u00f0ila skulu vera m.a. fulltr\u00faar fr\u00e1 N\u00e1tt\u00faruverndarstofnun, Ve\u00f0urstofu \u00cdslands, Skipulagsstofnun,[MAYBE-SPLIT]Fiskistofu, Hafranns\u00f3knastofnun, Samg\u00f6ngustofu, Landi og sk\u00f3gi, N\u00e1tt\u00farufr\u00e6\u00f0istofnun, Matv\u00e6lastofnun, H\u00fasn\u00e6\u00f0is- og mannvirkjastofnun, Vegager\u00f0inni, n\u00e1tt\u00farustofum og heilbrig\u00f0iseftirliti sveitarf\u00e9laga.": false, "R\u00e1\u00f0herra getur, a\u00f0 fenginni ums\u00f6gn Fiskistofu, Matv\u00e6lastofnunar,[MAYBE-SPLIT]Hafranns\u00f3knastofnunar og vi\u00f0komandi sveitarstj\u00f3rnar, takmarka\u00f0 e\u00f0a banna\u00f0 fiskeldi e\u00f0a \u00e1kve\u00f0nar eldisa\u00f0fer\u00f0ir \u00ed einstaka fj\u00f6r\u00f0um, fl\u00f3um e\u00f0a \u00e1 sv\u00e6\u00f0um sem teljast s\u00e9rlega vi\u00f0kv\u00e6m gagnvart starfsemi \u00feeirri sem fram fer samkv\u00e6mt l\u00f6gum \u00feessum.": false, "\u00c1\u00f0ur en leyfi skv. 1. mgr. er veitt getur Matv\u00e6lastofnun afla\u00f0 umsagnar Fiskistofu,[MAYBE-SPLIT]Hafranns\u00f3knastofnunar og vi\u00f0komandi sveitarstj\u00f3rnar eftir \u00fev\u00ed sem vi\u00f0 \u00e1 um hvort n\u00e1tt\u00farulegar a\u00f0st\u00e6\u00f0ur \u00e1 fyrirhugu\u00f0u starfssv\u00e6\u00f0i fiskeldisst\u00f6\u00f0var e\u00f0a fyrirhuga\u00f0ar eldistegundir, eldisstofnar e\u00f0a eldisa\u00f0fer\u00f0ir gefi tilefni til neikv\u00e6\u00f0ra vistfr\u00e6\u00f0i- e\u00f0a erf\u00f0afr\u00e6\u00f0i\u00e1hrifa sem leitt getur af leyfisskyldri starfsemi.": false, "Matv\u00e6lastofnun er heimilt, a\u00f0 fenginni ums\u00f6gn[MAYBE-SPLIT]Hafranns\u00f3knastofnunar, a\u00f0 \u00e1kve\u00f0a fri\u00f0unarsv\u00e6\u00f0i \u00ed sj\u00f3 framan vi\u00f0 fr\u00e1rennsli fiskeldisst\u00f6\u00f0va me\u00f0 s\u00f6mu skilyr\u00f0um og kve\u00f0i\u00f0 er \u00e1 um \u00ed 5. mgr. 15. gr. og 16. gr. laga um lax- og silungsvei\u00f0i.": false, "Umhverfis- og orkustofnun, N\u00e1tt\u00farufr\u00e6\u00f0istofnun,[MAYBE-SPLIT]Hafranns\u00f3knastofnun, landl\u00e6knisemb\u00e6tti\u00f0, Samg\u00f6ngustofa, Vegager\u00f0in, heilbrig\u00f0isnefndir sveitarf\u00e9laganna, Landhelgisg\u00e6sla \u00cdslands, hafnarstj\u00f3rnir, r\u00edkisl\u00f6greglustj\u00f3ri og Geislavarnir r\u00edkisins eru r\u00e1\u00f0herra til r\u00e1\u00f0gjafar um \u00feau atri\u00f0i sem a\u00f0 l\u00f6gum \u00feessum l\u00fata og heyra undir starfsemi \u00feeirra.": false, "Nemi pers\u00f3nuafsl\u00e1ttur skv. 1. mgr. h\u00e6rri fj\u00e1rh\u00e6\u00f0 en reikna\u00f0ur tekjuskattur af tekjuskattsstofni skv. 1. t\u00f6lul. 1. mgr. 66. gr. skal r\u00edkissj\u00f3\u00f0ur leggja fram f\u00e9 sem nemur allt a\u00f0 \u00feeim mun, og skal \u00fev\u00ed r\u00e1\u00f0stafa\u00f0 fyrir hvern mann til a\u00f0 grei\u00f0a \u00fatsvar hans \u00e1 \u00e1lagningar\u00e1rinu[MAYBE-SPLIT]S\u00e1 pers\u00f3nuafsl\u00e1ttur, sem \u00fe\u00e1 er enn \u00f3r\u00e1\u00f0stafa\u00f0, fellur ni\u00f0ur nema um s\u00e9 a\u00f0 r\u00e6\u00f0a \u00f3r\u00e1\u00f0stafa\u00f0an pers\u00f3nuafsl\u00e1tt annars hj\u00f3na, sem skattlagt er samkv\u00e6mt \u00e1kv\u00e6\u00f0um 62. gr., og skal \u00fe\u00e1 \u00f3r\u00e1\u00f0st\u00f6fu\u00f0um pers\u00f3nuafsl\u00e6tti annars makans b\u00e6tt vi\u00f0 pers\u00f3nuafsl\u00e1tt hins.": true, "Nemi \u00feannig \u00e1kvar\u00f0a\u00f0ur pers\u00f3nuafsl\u00e1ttur s\u00ed\u00f0arnefnda makans \u00ed heild h\u00e6rri fj\u00e1rh\u00e6\u00f0 en reikna\u00f0ur skattur af tekjuskattsstofni hans skv. 1. t\u00f6lul. 1. mgr. 66. gr. skal r\u00edkissj\u00f3\u00f0ur leggja fram f\u00e9 sem nemur allt a\u00f0 \u00feeim mun til a\u00f0 grei\u00f0a \u00fatsvar hans \u00e1 \u00e1lagningar\u00e1rinu[MAYBE-SPLIT]S\u00e1 hluti pers\u00f3nuafsl\u00e1ttar, sem \u00fe\u00e1 ver\u00f0ur enn \u00f3r\u00e1\u00f0stafa\u00f0, fellur ni\u00f0ur.": true, "Nemi \u00feannig \u00e1kvar\u00f0a\u00f0ur pers\u00f3nuafsl\u00e1ttur s\u00ed\u00f0arnefnda makans \u00ed heild h\u00e6rri fj\u00e1rh\u00e6\u00f0 en reikna\u00f0ur skattur af tekjuskattsstofni hans skv. 1. t\u00f6lul. 1. mgr. 66. gr. skal r\u00edkissj\u00f3\u00f0ur leggja fram f\u00e9 sem nemur allt a\u00f0 \u00feeim mun til a\u00f0 grei\u00f0a \u00fatsvar hans \u00e1 \u00e1lagningar\u00e1rinu .SPLIT[MAYBE-SPLIT]S\u00e1 hluti pers\u00f3nuafsl\u00e1ttar, sem \u00fe\u00e1 ver\u00f0ur enn \u00f3r\u00e1\u00f0stafa\u00f0, fellur ni\u00f0ur.": true, "H\u00f6fn sem n\u00fdtur r\u00edkisstyrks er skylt a\u00f0 senda endursko\u00f0a\u00f0a \u00e1rsreikninga s\u00edna \u00e1rlega til[MAYBE-SPLIT]Vegager\u00f0arinnar sem og a\u00f0rar uppl\u00fdsingar sem stofnunin kann a\u00f0 \u00f3ska eftir og snerta rekstur hafnarinnar.": false, "<i> Leyfishafi </i> merkir \u00ed l\u00f6gum \u00feessum skr\u00e1\u00f0ur a\u00f0ili h\u00e9r \u00e1 landi sem fengi\u00f0 hefur leyfi til ranns\u00f3knar og/e\u00f0a vinnslu kolvetnis skv.[MAYBE-SPLIT]IV. kafla.": false, "\u00c1\u00f0ur en veitt er ranns\u00f3knar- og vinnsluleyfi, sam\u00feykki e\u00f0a leyfi fyrir einst\u00f6kum framkv\u00e6mdum skv. 14.\u201318. gr. skal Umhverfis- og orkustofnun leita umsagnar[MAYBE-SPLIT]N\u00e1tt\u00farufr\u00e6\u00f0istofnunar, H\u00fasn\u00e6\u00f0is- og mannvirkjastofnunar og Hafranns\u00f3knastofnunar.": false, "Vi\u00f0 veitingu leyfis skv.[MAYBE-SPLIT]IV. kafla skal \u00feess g\u00e6tt a\u00f0 n\u00fdting au\u00f0lindanna s\u00e9 me\u00f0 \u00feeim h\u00e6tti a\u00f0 teki\u00f0 s\u00e9 tillit til umhverfissj\u00f3narmi\u00f0a, n\u00fdting au\u00f0lindanna s\u00e9 hagkv\u00e6m fr\u00e1 \u00fej\u00f3\u00f0hagslegu sj\u00f3narmi\u00f0i og teki\u00f0 s\u00e9 tillit til n\u00fdtingar sem \u00feegar er hafin \u00ed n\u00e6sta n\u00e1grenni.": false, "\u00c1\u00f0ur en leyfi er veitt skal leita umsagnar[MAYBE-SPLIT]N\u00e1tt\u00faruverndarstofnunar, N\u00e1tt\u00farufr\u00e6\u00f0istofnunar og eftir atvikum Hafranns\u00f3knastofnunar.": false, "\u00datgefandi starfsleyfis skal tilgreina \u00ed starfsleyfi, sbr. vi\u00f0auka[MAYBE-SPLIT]IV, rekstrara\u00f0ila og sta\u00f0setningu starfsemi, tegund hennar og st\u00e6r\u00f0 og skilyr\u00f0i, auk \u00e1kv\u00e6\u00f0a um vi\u00f0mi\u00f0unarm\u00f6rk, orkun\u00fdtingu, me\u00f0fer\u00f0 \u00fargangs, mengunarvarnir, tilkynningarskyldu vegna \u00f3happa e\u00f0a slysa, innra eftirlit, v\u00f6ktun, eftirlitsm\u00e6lingar og ranns\u00f3knir, svo og rekstur og vi\u00f0hald mengunarvarnab\u00fana\u00f0ar, eftir \u00fev\u00ed sem vi\u00f0 \u00e1 hverju sinni.": false, "L\u00e1n sem \u00e1h\u00e6ttugjald skv. 4. gr. hefur veri\u00f0 greitt af, skuldbindingar vegna innst\u00e6\u00f0na \u00e1 innl\u00e1nsreikningum \u00ed innl\u00e1nsstofnunum, skuldbindingar vegna \u00fatflutnings\u00e1byrg\u00f0a me\u00f0 r\u00edkis\u00e1byrg\u00f0, Se\u00f0labanki \u00cdslands, \u00cdb\u00fa\u00f0al\u00e1nasj\u00f3\u00f0ur,[MAYBE-SPLIT]H\u00fasn\u00e6\u00f0is- og mannvirkjastofnun og L\u00e1nasj\u00f3\u00f0ur \u00edslenskra n\u00e1msmanna eru undan\u00feegin grei\u00f0slu \u00e1byrg\u00f0argjalds skv. 6. gr.": false, "Undan\u00feegnir skyldu skv. 1. mgr. eru: erlend r\u00edki og al\u00fej\u00f3\u00f0astofnanir, Afur\u00f0asj\u00f3\u00f0ur Grindav\u00edkurb\u00e6jar, Menntasj\u00f3\u00f0ur n\u00e1msmanna, Bygg\u00f0astofnun, Byggingarsj\u00f3\u00f0ur r\u00edkisins, Byggingarsj\u00f3\u00f0ur verkamanna, \u00cdb\u00fa\u00f0al\u00e1nasj\u00f3\u00f0ur,[MAYBE-SPLIT]H\u00fasn\u00e6\u00f0is- og mannvirkjastofnun, Framkv\u00e6mdasj\u00f3\u00f0ur fatla\u00f0ra, Framkv\u00e6mdasj\u00f3\u00f0ur aldra\u00f0ra, Matv\u00e6lasj\u00f3\u00f0ur, N\u00fdsk\u00f6punarsj\u00f3\u00f0urinn Kr\u00eda, Fiskr\u00e6ktarsj\u00f3\u00f0ur, Happdr\u00e6tti H\u00e1sk\u00f3la \u00cdslands, L\u00e1nasj\u00f3\u00f0ur sveitarf\u00e9laga ohf. og L\u00e1nasj\u00f3\u00f0ur Vestur-Nor\u00f0urlanda, Se\u00f0labanki \u00cdslands, sj\u00f3\u00f0ir sem starfa samkv\u00e6mt l\u00f6gum um ver\u00f0br\u00e9fasj\u00f3\u00f0i og l\u00f6gum um rekstrara\u00f0ila s\u00e9rh\u00e6f\u00f0ra sj\u00f3\u00f0a, l\u00e1nastofnanir sem skattskyldar eru samkv\u00e6mt l\u00f6gum nr. 65/1982, me\u00f0 s\u00ed\u00f0ari breytingum, ver\u00f0br\u00e9fafyrirt\u00e6ki, sbr. l\u00f6g um marka\u00f0i fyrir fj\u00e1rm\u00e1lagerninga, ver\u00f0br\u00e9fami\u00f0st\u00f6\u00f0var, sbr. l\u00f6g um rafr\u00e6na eignarskr\u00e1ningu ver\u00f0br\u00e9fa, nr. 131/1997, l\u00edftryggingaf\u00e9l\u00f6g, sbr. 23. gr. laga nr. 60/1994, og l\u00edfeyrissj\u00f3\u00f0ir, sbr. l\u00f6g um skyldutryggingu l\u00edfeyrisr\u00e9ttinda og starfsemi l\u00edfeyrissj\u00f3\u00f0a, og starfstengdir eftirlaunasj\u00f3\u00f0ir, sbr. l\u00f6g um starfstengda eftirlaunasj\u00f3\u00f0i.": false, "Sektir geta numi\u00f0 fr\u00e1 100 \u00fe\u00fas. kr. til 100 millj. kr.[MAYBE-SPLIT]Sektar\u00e1kv\u00f6r\u00f0un samkv\u00e6mt \u00e1kv\u00e6\u00f0i \u00feessu skal loki\u00f0 innan sex m\u00e1na\u00f0a fr\u00e1 \u00fev\u00ed a\u00f0 ranns\u00f3kn skattranns\u00f3knarstj\u00f3ra lauk.": true, "\u00d3heimilt er a\u00f0 hefja rekstur \u00ed fyrirt\u00e6ki e\u00f0a hluta fyrirt\u00e6kis fyrr en eftirlitsma\u00f0ur hefur gefi\u00f0 r\u00e9ttum a\u00f0ilum vottor\u00f0 um, a\u00f0 allur \u00fatb\u00fana\u00f0ur s\u00e9 \u00ed fullu lagi og \u00ed samr\u00e6mi vi\u00f0 fyrirm\u00e6li forstj\u00f3ra[MAYBE-SPLIT]Vinnueftirlits r\u00edkisins, a\u00f0 mati eftirlitsmannsins.": false}